# Cursor Rules â€” Node Admin

Aturan lengkap & wajib: lihat AGENTS.md (sumber kebenaran). Ringkas:

- Ikuti alur: route â†’ handler(DI) â†’ controller(@injectable, inject IService) â†’ service(@injectable, implements IService, throw AppError) â†’ repository(inject) â†’ entity.
- DILARANG: `new XService()/XController()` di routes (pakai `handler()`); `return error`/`instanceof Error` (pakai `throw AppError`); `res.render(path.resolve(...))` (pakai `renderView()`); `process.env` di src/modules (pakai `env` dari config/env); tipe kolom vendor (`longtext`/`datetime`) atau `@CreateDateColumn({type})`.
- Service WAJIB `@injectable` + punya interface `I*Service` + constructor injection dual-mode.
- Modul/fitur baru: ikuti docs/MODULE_GUIDE.md; tambah test + update README/docs/API.md.
- Sebelum selesai: `npm run lint:conventions`, `npx tsc --noEmit`, `npm test` harus lolos.
- Security: urutan middleware ensureAuthenticatedâ†’AccessMiddleware; CSRF di form; rate-limit endpoint sensitif; Joi stripUnknown.
